    <string name="settings_about_version">Version %1$s (%2$d)</string>
    <string name="settings_about_privacy">Your Gemini API key is encrypted at rest using a key bound to the Android Keystore. Forecasts come from Open-Meteo (no key, no account); the daily summary text is generated by Gemini. AdaptWeather does not have a backend — nothing is sent to any server we control.</string>
